kasuga_freeter.name: Yakuza
kasuga_freeter.explain: Ichiban Kasuga's exclusive job. Relies on good old hand to hand combat. Capable of learning moves befitting of a new dragon.

kasuga_braver.name: Hero
kasuga_braver.explain: Ichiban Kasuga's exclusive job. Fights using a bat like a sword. Can attack with a good range and moderate damage, but really shines with all support skills.

nanba_01.name: Homeless Guy
nanba_01.explain: Yu Nanba's exclusive job. Fights using umbrellas and canes. Capable of learning homeless tricks like fire breathing, pigeon control, and smelly breaths!

adachi_01.name: Detective
adachi_01.explain: Koichi Adachi's exclusive job. Focuses on beatdown, taking aggro from enemies to protect allies and  using extremely powerful attacks based on Adachi's HP.

saeko_01.name: Barmaid
saeko_01.explain: Saeko's exclusive job. Smacks enemies with a handbag and capable of learning strong martial arts.

jyungi_01.name: Hitman
jyungi_01.explain: Joon-gi Han's exclusive job. Uses brass knuckles, assassination techniques, karambits and pistols.

chou_01.name: Gangster
chou_01.explain: Tianyou Zhao's exclusive job. Fights with saber and Chinese Kenpo martial arts. Normal attacks can inflict bleed.

woman_a_01.name: Clerk
woman_a_01.explain: Eri Kamataki exclusive job. Cuts down enemies with a box cutter. Capable of learning speedy physical attacks with an arsenal of office supplies.

man_01.name: Bodyguard
man_01.explain: Excels with a katana. Capable of learning techniques that harm oneself to inflict even worse pain on the enemy.

man_02.name: Host
man_02.explain: Brings a whole new meaning to bottle service. Capable of learning special host techniques to stay cool and collected while toppling enemies or stealing their shit.

man_kaitaiya.name: Foreman
man_kaitaiya.explain: Wields a mighty hammer to get the job done. Capable of learning techniques to crush anything and everything that stands in the way!

man_musician.name: Musician
man_musician.explain: Takes on the world with a trusty guitar and the power of music to inspire your allies or dampen the enemy's fighting spirit. Songs increases your voltage. Skill Attacks resets the voltage to zero.

man_05.name: Breaker
man_05.explain: Pops, locks, and drops the enemies to the floor. Capable of learning a variety of funky fresh dance techniques to toy with and take down the enemy.

man_06.name: Enforcer
man_06.explain: Employs standard-issue shields and batons. Capable of learning techniques to protect one's allies or overwhelm one's foes.

man_07.name: Chef
man_07.explain: Brings the heat from the kitchen to the street! Get ready to dish out bleeding and burn to enemies. Tactical usage of skills can make this job vanquish enemies in no time.

man_08.name: Fortuneteller
man_08.explain: Allows one to use miraculous powers to bless allies and curse enemies. Comes with elemental attacks to overwhelm enemies.

woman_idol.name: Idol
woman_idol.explain: Uses a microphone to heal allies, remove status afflictions and charm enemies with cutesy movements. A must have job for harder battles.

woman_02.name: Hostess
woman_02.explain: Fights enemies with a makeup pouch. Capable of learning special hostess skills to deal with all types of enemies.

woman_dealer.name: Dealer
woman_dealer.explain: Leaves it all to the cards and the divine will of lady luck. Capable of learning very hit-or-miss techniques that can turn the tables in the blink of an eye!

woman_nightqueen.name: Night Queen
woman_nightqueen.explain: Uses Whips, violent kicks and lewd services to bring both pain and pleasure to enemies and allies. Excels at brainwashing and silencing enemies.

dlc_01.name: Devil Rocker
dlc_01.explain: Unleashes all hell through the power of rock. Making one proclaim to be the Devil himself, it's capable of learning techniques that torment enemies with highly destructive performances, consequences be damned.

woman_martial.name: Matriarch
woman_martial.explain: Swings around a naginata with unmatched style and grace. Capable of learning a vast repertoire of attacks that catch enemies within their exceptionally long reach.
